00:18:36.510 --> 00:18:37.945 align:middle line:90%
Is there some practice to heal?

00:18:37.945 --> 00:18:41.670 align:middle line:84%
Or is it just really just
continuing to remember this

00:18:41.670 --> 00:18:43.507 align:middle line:90%
and to trust, trust, trust?

00:18:43.507 --> 00:18:45.840 align:middle line:84%
>> SINGH: We talked about the
fountain of youth earlier.

00:18:45.840 --> 00:18:50.597 align:middle line:84%
