00:19:00.690 --> 00:19:02.148 align:middle line:84%
None of us are
supposed to do that.

00:19:02.148 --> 00:19:04.790 align:middle line:84%
Because it's all divine,
so it can heal itself.

00:19:04.790 --> 00:19:06.400 align:middle line:84%
There's also nothing
to save, fix,

00:19:06.400 --> 00:19:09.010 align:middle line:90%
or heal in here for any of us.

00:19:09.010 --> 00:19:10.200 align:middle line:90%
It's all divine.

00:19:10.200 --> 00:19:12.040 align:middle line:90%
It can shift at any moment.

00:19:12.040 --> 00:19:15.870 align:middle line:84%
What we are to do is to dive
into our hearts and our guts

00:19:15.870 --> 00:19:18.100 align:middle line:84%
and really tap into that
dream that we've always

00:19:18.100 --> 00:19:20.460 align:middle line:84%
wanted that we've never
allowed ourselves.

00:19:20.460 --> 00:19:23.510 align:middle line:84%
And when we do that, the
unique genius bubbles up

00:19:23.510 --> 00:19:26.160 align:middle line:84%
from each one of us,
and that inspiration

00:19:26.160 --> 00:19:29.170 align:middle line:84%
is going to solve the pains
and the ills of the world,

00:19:29.170 --> 00:19:31.010 align:middle line:84%
because it's going
to be inspired,

00:19:31.010 --> 00:19:32.510 align:middle line:84%
rather than what
we're trying to do,

00:19:32.510 --> 00:19:33.850 align:middle line:90%
which is think up the solutions.

00:19:33.850 --> 00:19:36.030 align:middle line:84%
We can't think our
way out of this,

00:19:36.030 --> 00:19:38.150 align:middle line:84%
because we thought
our way into it.

00:19:38.150 --> 00:19:39.530 align:middle line:90%
But we can inspire.

00:19:39.530 --> 00:19:42.490 align:middle line:84%
We can breathe life into
ourselves and, in turn,

00:19:42.490 --> 00:19:44.700 align:middle line:84%
bring life into the
world around us.

00:19:44.700 --> 00:19:47.230 align:middle line:84%
And that's what's going
to create the change.

00:19:47.230 --> 00:19:48.855 align:middle line:84%
>> LILOU: Tell us
about this number 11.

