3/11, 9/11, 11/11 everywhere.

00:20:08.377 --> 00:20:10.460 align:middle line:84%
>> SINGH: This is how I
discovered that there were

00:20:10.460 --> 00:20:11.620 align:middle line:90%
conversations.

00:20:11.620 --> 00:20:13.650 align:middle line:84%
