that life could break through,

00:20:19.900 --> 00:20:21.970 align:middle line:84%
the universe started
sending me 11's, 1:11's

00:20:21.970 --> 00:20:24.851 align:middle line:84%
and 11:11's 25 to
30 times a day.

00:20:24.851 --> 00:20:26.100 align:middle line:90%
I didn't know what they meant.

00:20:26.100 --> 00:20:27.516 align:middle line:84%
They just showed
up on everything,

00:20:27.516 --> 00:20:29.670 align:middle line:84%
from trains and
bulldozers and buses

00:20:29.670 --> 00:20:33.470 align:middle line:84%
