create it, to do this now.

00:20:45.690 --> 00:20:47.540 align:middle line:84%
You will heal and
others will heal.

00:20:47.540 --> 00:20:52.279 align:middle line:84%
But I also got the download that
11 is the gateway of mastery

00:20:52.279 --> 00:20:53.820 align:middle line:84%
and that there are
millions of people

00:20:53.820 --> 00:20:55.250 align:middle line:90%
around the world that see it.

00:20:55.250 --> 00:20:56.750 align:middle line:84%
And it is a symbol
that's showing up

00:20:56.750 --> 00:21:00.190 align:middle line:84%
to usher us to understand
that there's not just physical

00:21:00.190 --> 00:21:03.680 align:middle line:84%
but there's spiritual, to move
out of negative into positive,

00:21:03.680 --> 00:21:07.490 align:middle line:84%
to understand that there's much
more to this world that is real

00:21:07.490 --> 00:21:12.180 align:middle line:84%
that is actually beyond what
we see that is the illusion.

00:21:12.180 --> 00:21:16.840 align:middle line:84%
And so as I began saying my
yes to doing this magazine,

00:21:16.840 --> 00:21:18.930 align:middle line:84%
I started to realize
there are many other ways

00:21:18.930 --> 00:21:20.770 align:middle line:90%
that the universe speaks to us.

00:21:20.770 --> 00:21:23.640 align:middle line:84%
See, we don't realize that
our pets and their ailments

00:21:23.640 --> 00:21:26.730 align:middle line:84%
are actually trying to show us
where we've blocked ourselves

00:21:26.730 --> 00:21:27.860 align:middle line:90%
in our own thinking.

00:21:27.860 --> 00:21:31.040 align:middle line:84%
Our children go through
specific experiences

00:21:31.040 --> 00:21:33.340 align:middle line:84%
in their lives at the
exact age that we're

00:21:33.340 --> 00:21:36.210 align:middle line:84%
supposed to go back and look
at our own life for that very

00:21:36.210 --> 00:21:39.030 align:middle line:84%
same emotional
issue to clear it.

00:21:39.030 --> 00:21:41.330 align:middle line:84%
That's how they show up
to teach us something.

00:21:41.330 --> 00:21:44.920 align:middle line:84%
Our homes, our cars, they
are each us showing us

00:21:44.920 --> 00:21:47.130 align:middle line:84%
something when something
happens to them.

00:21:47.130 --> 00:21:49.080 align:middle line:84%
And if we start to ask
those questions that I

00:21:49.080 --> 00:21:51.330 align:middle line:84%
talk about in "Conversations
with the Universe,"

00:21:51.330 --> 00:21:54.460 align:middle line:84%
where is that in me, what
is this trying to show me

00:21:54.460 --> 00:21:57.140 align:middle line:84%
about me, what is
the gift inside of me

00:21:57.140 --> 00:21:59.790 align:middle line:84%
that is trying to be released
that has been dormant,

00:21:59.790 --> 00:22:02.910 align:middle line:84%
all of a sudden we clean and
clear this inner landscape

00:22:02.910 --> 00:22:05.340 align:middle line:84%
and shift our outer
landscape and discover

00:22:05.340 --> 00:22:06.880 align:middle line:90%
more of our divine presence.

00:22:06.880 --> 00:22:09.530 align:middle line:84%
And that's how we will move
more and more into the presence

00:22:09.530 --> 00:22:11.990 align:middle line:84%
of now where we're not
living in the future,

00:22:11.990 --> 00:22:14.330 align:middle line:84%
we're not living in the
past, we rid ourselves

00:22:14.330 --> 00:22:16.600 align:middle line:84%
of all fear and
anxiety and depression,

00:22:16.600 --> 00:22:18.670 align:middle line:84%
and we truly are
present in the moment.

